videos.headline: Darius Phillips 75 Yd Interception Return
videos.description: Darius Phillips 75 Yd Interception Return (Butch Hampton Kick)

videos.headline: Western Michigan scores game's first TD on pick-six
videos.description: Western Michigan cornerback Darius Phillips skies for the interception and takes it back all the way for a touchdown to give the Broncos a 7-0 lead over Ball State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Western Michigan scores game's first TD on pick-six) 2016/11/1

videos.headline: Jarvion Franklin 23 Yd Run
videos.description: Jarvion Franklin 23 Yd Run (Butch Hampton Kick)

videos.headline: Davis left wide open on 57-yard Western Michigan TD
videos.description: Western Michigan quarterback Zach Terrell lofts a ball down the middle of the field to wide receiver Corey Davis for a 57-yard touchdown to give the Broncos a 21-7 lead over Ball State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Davis left wide open on 57-yard Western Michigan TD) 2016/11/01

videos.headline: WMU's Davis jumps over Ball State's defender for second TD
videos.description: Western Michigan quarterback Zach Terrell underthrows Corey Davis, but Davis jumps over the Ball State defender to score a 35-yard touchdown for the Broncos to increase their lead to 28-10.

videos.headline: J. Milas pass intercepted by J. Ferguson
videos.description: Jack Milas pass intercepted Justin Ferguson return for no gain to the WMich 13

videos.headline: M. Hagee 44 yd FG BLOCKED,blocked by Broncos
videos.description: Morgan Hagee 44 yd FG BLOCKED blocked by Broncos

videos.headline: WMU's Davis eludes three Ball State defenders for third TD
videos.description: Zach Terrell continues to look for Corey Davis, and Davis does not disappoint, going 62 yards and breaking several tackles to score his third touchdown to extend Western Michigan's lead to 35-10 over Ball State.

videos.headline: Western Michigan turns in dominant performance against Ball State
videos.description: Ray Bentley and Dave Lamont break down Western Michigan's victory over Ball State.

videos.headline: No. 23 Western Michigan rolls on Davis' big day
videos.description: Corey Davis catches 12 passes for 272 yards and three touchdowns as No. 23 Western Michigan thrashes Ball State 52-20.
